d above.</p><h3> <strong>The February 2025 Xbox Game Pass titles are:</strong></h3><p> <em><strong>18 – Avowed (Ultimate, PC)</strong></em><br /> <em><strong>20 – EA Sports F1 24 (Ultimate, PC)</strong></em><br /> <em><strong>20 – Warhammer 40,000: Rogue Trader (Ultimate, PC, Standard)</strong></em><br /> <em><strong>20 – Watch Dogs: Legion (Ultimate, PC, Standard)</strong></em></p><blockquote class="twitter-tweet" data-width="550" data-dnt="true"><p lang="en" dir="ltr"> hope this coming soon posts finds you well <a href="https://t.co/Z0BXrzmhDA">https://t.co/Z0BXrzmhDA</a> <a href="https://t.co/VMzsS2CjCd">pic.twitter.com/VMzsS2CjCd</a></p><p> — Xbox Game Pass (@XboxGamePass) <a href="https://twitter.com/XboxGamePass/status/1891850234990415943?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">February 18, 2025</a> </p></blockquote><p><script async src="https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p> A number of titles will also be leaving Xbox Game Pass at the end of February, so you&#39;ve only got until the 28th to play the following for free:</p><p> <em><strong>F1 22</strong></em><br /><em><strong>格里斯</strong></em><br /><em><strong>人民者</strong></em><br /><em><strong>爪子巡逻世界</strong></em><br /><em><strong>太空工程师</strong></em><br /><em><strong>Warhammer 40,000: Boltgun</strong></em><br /> <em><strong>Wo Long Fallen Dynasty</strong></em><br /> <em><strong>Yakuza 3 Remastered</strong></em><br /> <em><strong>Yakuza 4重新制作</strong></em></p><p>In the coming months, Game Pass subscribers will get access to <em><a href="https://www.nme.com/games/atomfall">Atomfall</a> , <a href="https://www.nme.com/games/south-of-midnight">South Of Midnight</a> , <a href="https://www.nme.com/games/clair-obscur-expedition-33">Clair Obscur: Expedition 33</a></em> and <em><a href="https://www.nme.com/games/doom-the-dark-ages">Doom: The Dark Ages</a> .</em></p><p> In other news, <em><a href="https://www.nme.com/games/grand-theft-auto-vi">Grand Theft Auto 6</a></em> publisher Take-Two has said <a h